# Task 2 - AI Powered Data Extraction

## Objective
Extract structured information from unstructured text and convert it into JSON format.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Regular Expressions (Regex)
- JSON

## Input
Unstructured text containing customer details such as name, date, and destination.

## Output
Structured JSON data extracted from the input text.

## Example Output

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "date": "25 July 2026",
  "destination": "Chennai"
}

